name: Fix your power cycle!
description:
In this game, your character crash landed because of lost a power cycle. Collect the power sources (stars) to restore it. I did not have time for an ending. So go for the high score!

Cheat codes:

Select the cheat codes menu option, click the text box, enter the code, press enter, then play. re-enter the cheats menu to disable it.
